{{#ifeq: {{{1|}}}|Telescope.Altitude| {{{!}} class="wikitable" ! Part ! Description {{!}}- {{!}} Value (Double) {{!}} The Altitude above the local horizon of the telescope's current position (degrees, positive up). {{|}}}
