Established convention uses "..." to seperate begin- and end tags with no content. Please replace:
<pre>
 |o|open
 |p|pair   = &gt;{{{content|}}}
</pre>
with:
<pre>
 |o|open   = &gt;{{{content|}}}
 |p|pair   = &gt;{{{content|...}}}
</pre>
